<L>__{ext day: mall (spring 1946)}
<A>__{the corleone mall. equally impressive security stands ready at the corleone mall. extra button men, as well as some police, and private}
<B>__{detectives.}
<A>__{it all seems to be under the supervision of rocco lampone. all is silent. the women and children, dressed in sunday clothes, wait.}
<L>__{ext day: ambulance (spring 1946)}
<A>__{one ambulance, speeding along the grand central parkway, preceded and followed by a dark car, each one carrying a team of button men. sitting next to the driver of the ambulance is a guard with a rifle on his lap.}
